  SF-ADJUSTMENT _"Relative distance of horizon" '(5 0.1 24.1 0.1 1 1 1)
  SF-ADJUSTMENT _"Relative length of shadow"    '(1 0.1 24   0.1 1 1 1)
  SF-ADJUSTMENT _"Blur radius"                  '(3 0 1024 1 10 0 0)
